news.title: Zika Symptoms May Vary, So Testing Is Crucial
news.summary: (HealthDay News) -- Zika infection isn't always obvious. In one recent case, a rash, bloodshot eyes and spots in the mouth were key symptoms of infection with the mosquito-borne virus, researchers report.
